{"tid":2075707,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有單據證件 警懶理照拉  架生被當非法用具 地盤管工脫罪","createTime":"2020-06-23T04:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T05:09:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bebfd543806c22fa29dfa1d2602584eaecb31f38","tid":2075707,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:32:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/4GTSE4M23L76TN4LNEVYN3OMDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2F4GTSE4M23L76TN4LNEVYN3OMDE%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7vdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=b5d9a25c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2F4GTSE4M23L76TN4LNEVYN3OMDE%2F&h=de473750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/4GTSE4M23L76TN4LNEVYN3OMDE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n有單據證件 警懶理照拉 <br />\n架生被當非法用具 地盤管工脫罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KRQZCSBFVJN2I7SUEXA7NUFTSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKRQZCSBFVJN2I7SUEXA7NUFTSI.jpg&h=c2f23662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年11月三罷期間，防暴警曾多次到銅鑼灣崇光百貨門外驅散示威者。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】地盤管工去年11月12日三罷期間在銅鑼灣被警方搜出身藏𠝹刀、石屎釘及石屎鑿等物品，遭拘控管有適合作非法用途工具罪。判頭昨不認罪受審。雖然涉案物品是常用地盤工具，被告亦解釋買來翌日開工用，有齊單據，身上有工作證，已講明在附近吃飯，但警員基於相信他曾經或企圖參與非法集結或破壞，不理解釋照拉照告。裁判官聽罷被告作供，認為他的解釋並非不可能，即日裁定被告脫罪。<br />\n<br />\n被告徐煒榤（23歲）被控藏有一把𠝹刀、一盒刀片、兩盒鐵釘和兩把鑿，原被控多一項藏毒罪，但1月時控方化驗涉案粉末後證實根本不是毒品而撤控。庭上首先播放被告在現場遭搜身的片段，被告在片中自稱是「地盤科文」，謂「我有合理需要買呢啲嘢，因為我地盤用」。其間有警員說：「唔需要喺度講！要解釋返差館講！」<br />\n<br />\n拘捕被告的警員陳。。。。。，認為被告形迹可疑遂截查。<br />\n<br />\n陳政賢稱，普通市民。。。。。獲悉相關資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告徐煒榤否認控罪受審，獲裁判官即日裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警認沒見被告作破壞行為<br />\n<br />\n陳又稱，相信被告曾。。。。。，惟他亦承認沒見被告曾作出任何相關行為。<br />\n<br />\n被告自辯時稱，他在旺角買石。。。。。，在路上遭警員截查。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官林希維裁決指接納。。。。。物品作非法用途，裁定他脫罪並可取回訟費。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2555/19"},{"pid":"8fd77eb381247c683397fc9458a7780a75f34557","tid":2075707,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"鳩告又唔洗負責任  <br />\n係美國? 政府一早賠一億比被告了"},{"pid":"c9d1dd6fd8d9cc318f34458c876342855d27fcf9","tid":2075707,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1df9f354bbc7031469528a59a0039e5dd0f7bc","tid":2075707,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:44:38.000Z","msg":"［行動Post］7月11-12日全香港要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2075714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2075714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"219777b5a244a40c447b50a1915ce726cc2c9866","tid":2075707,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98974189cb4adf1fc4a5e1b48bfaa8c7c056887f","tid":2075707,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"脫罪又點，俾黑警blacklist一定仲有下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：揾人跟蹤同自製黑材料&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"befd0ce87e42956402da64ea008c9832896d8160","tid":2075707,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />call黑警去三跑拉晒佢<br />\n好多武器係果到"}]}